{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_01_05",
  "title": "LizNoir 01 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央ちゃーん！　莉央ちゃあああああんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-chan! Rio-chaaaaan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.910232293605804,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.666666666666,
          "startTime": 5.866666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirサイコー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir is the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.910232293605804,
      "endTime": 7.676371669769287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葵ーっ！　俺だーっ！　結婚してくれーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi~! It's me~! Marry me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.876371669769287,
      "endTime": 12.103265142440797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.303265142440797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "どうも、ありがとうございました！\nこれからも応援よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all very much!\nWe hope for your continued support!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.303265142440797,
      "endTime": 18.02299294471741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.236598475774098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "どうも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.23659847577413,
      "endTime": 19.203763993581138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1167.1655178070068,
          "startTime": 19.403763993581137
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.403763993581137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――デビューからしばらく経ち、LizNoirは新人とは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after their debut‚ LizNoir were attracting attention",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.403763993581137,
      "endTime": 23.183764102520087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思えないレベルの高いパフォーマンスで注目されていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for their high level performances that defied their rookie status.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.18376410252008,
      "endTime": 26.68376420338948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "新人アイドルとしては順調な滑り出しと言っていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It could be said that they had gotten off to a good start as rookie idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8704306602478,
      "endTime": 30.09043063587612,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 899.9999999999986,
          "startTime": 27.770430660247797
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.09043063587612,
      "endTime": 31.037097326914463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 31.9704306602478
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 31.970430660247832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、葵\nさっきのアレはなんなのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Aoi!\nWhat was that just now?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.33709732691446,
      "endTime": 36.64235803286233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 36.837097326914474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "アレって何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What was \"that\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.837097326914474,
      "endTime": 38.19575950304668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "最後の挨拶よ！　デビューしたばかりの私達のライブを\n見に来てくれた大切なファンなのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our final greeting! Those were precious fans\nwho came to see our live‚ even though we just debuted!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.39575950304668,
      "endTime": 45.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 45.56242616971333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "もっと愛想良く出来ないの？　もっと笑うの！\nせっかく可愛いのに、そんなんじゃ魅力半減よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't you be a little nicer? Smile more!\nYou're wasting your cuteness by acting like that‚ you're halving your charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.56242616971333,
      "endTime": 53.23718822797139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 53.46242616971334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "いつ笑うかなんて僕の自由だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I smile is up to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.46242616971334,
      "endTime": 55.98408153851827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 56.18408153851827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "笑顔を振りまくのもアイドルの仕事のうちよ\n葵がそんな意識じゃ私達はもっと上に行けないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Smiling is part of an idol's job.\nIf you don't understand that‚ Aoi‚ we won't be able to reach greater heights.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.18408153851827,
      "endTime": 64.30387762387593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "上って、何？\n莉央もうデビューしたし給料も出てるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Greater heights? What are you talking about?\nRio‚ we debuted‚ and we're getting paid‚ aren't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5174148718516,
      "endTime": 69.67634927431742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 69.88408153851823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirとしてデビュー後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After debuting as LizNoir‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9,
      "endTime": 72.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央はようやく母親に仕送りが出来るようになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio was finally able to send allowance to her mother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 75.62408163528129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 75.81741487185157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だが、実家の事情を考えればまだ足りない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ considering her family situation‚ it was still not enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.81741487185157,
      "endTime": 78.47741482655204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "母と喫茶店を守るために、もっと稼ぎたかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wanted to earn more to protect her mother and the cafe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.48408153851825,
      "endTime": 81.42408148845035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 81.61741487185158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "こんな小さなライブハウスすら満員に\n出来ていないのよ！　この程度のアイドルでいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't even fill up a small live house like this!\nAre you okay with being this level of idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.61741487185158,
      "endTime": 87.67857143084206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "葵だって\nもっと大きな会場でライブしたいでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to perform at a bigger venue‚\ndon't you‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.88979919906552,
      "endTime": 91.76519597526486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 91.9897991990655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕は歌って踊れればそれでいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine as long as I can sing and dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9897991990655,
      "endTime": 95.43979929443293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 95.63979929443293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "それより、莉央のダンスまた少し重くなってるよ\n僕の笑顔より、そっちの方が問題じゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ your dancing has gotten a bit heavy again‚ Rio.\nIsn't that more of a problem than my smile?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.63979929443293,
      "endTime": 102.7397994851678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 102.93979929443297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "うっ\n……気を付けるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh.\n…I'll be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.93979929443297,
      "endTime": 106.70113709922728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.90646596109963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんが葵を組ませた理由が今ではよく分かる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Now I understand why Saegusa-san paired me with Aoi.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.90646596109963,
      "endTime": 111.35646605646707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "（葵は軽くて自由、それが魅力）\n（だけどあまりにも自由過ぎて危うい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Aoi is light and free‚ that's her charm.)\n(But she's so free that she's dangerous.)",
